	Author = {Alexey Jakovlevich Chervonenkis},
	Abstract = {In the paper the problem of conditional distribution estimation at a current point on tha basis of measured values of a random field at a set of sampling points is considered. An estimator is searched in the form similar to Parsen estimation of a distribution function, but with coefficients depending on the distance between the current point and the sampling points. Theoretical foundation is given for optimal choice of these coefficients. Application of the theory are considered in the learning theory and practical problems. },
